## Scoring Rubric

| Rating | Description | Criteria |
|--------|-------------|----------|
| **4 - Exemplary** | Exceeds expectations | Deep understanding, applies concepts to novel situations |
| **3 - Proficient** | Meets expectations | Correctly applies tools and methods, accurate interpretation |
| **2 - Developing** | Approaching expectations | Partial understanding, some tool usage errors |
| **1 - Beginning** | Below expectations | Significant gaps, unable to apply tools without guidance |

## Phase Gate Summary

| Phase | Minimum Checkpoints | Gate Criteria |
|-------|---------------------|---------------|
| Define | 3 | Charter and MGPP submitted |
| Measure | 4 | Statistical analysis validated |
| Explore | 5 | FMEA completed |
| Develop | 5 | DOE report submitted |
| Implement | 3 | Capstone project submitted |

